secondary_outcome.description:
The humoral immune response will be assessed for bioCSL QIV & comparator QIV. Serum HI titers against the 4 influenza vaccine strains will be used to calculate:
Geometric mean of HI titers prevaccination & postvaccination;
SCRs: % of subjects with either a prevaccination HI titer < 1:10 and a postvaccination HI titer ≥ 1:40 or a prevaccination titer ≥ 1:10 and a ≥ 4-fold increase in postvaccination titer;
The % of subjects with a titer ≥40 (seroprotection rates) at Day 1 and at Exit Visit;
Geometric mean fold increase (GMFI): geometric mean fold titer rise from Day 1 to Exit Visit.

